Class Sentence

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.ornl.csed.csiir.sava.stucco.models.Sentence

  • public class Sentence
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an annotated sentence from unstructured text. This representation includes a list of words, part of speech tags, I-O-B formatting tags, and domain-specific terms.
